Enum Mode backed by u8 has idle be 0; active be 1; failed be 2.

To count active modes modes: view of Mode, giving i32.
Let active be 0.
Let failed be 0.
For each index i of modes:
Match modes at i:
Mode.active: active becomes active plus 1;
Mode.failed: failed becomes failed plus 1;
otherwise: active becomes active.
Give active plus failed.

To main, giving i32.
Let modes be array of 4 Mode containing Mode.idle, Mode.active, Mode.failed, Mode.active.
Give count active modes modes.
